You are implementing Task 6, 7, and 8 for the frontend (collabspace-web).

## Task 6: Frontend types and conversion

### File 1: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-web/packages/web/types/announcement.ts`

Current content:
```typescript
export type IAnnouncementItem = {
  publishTime: string;
  title: string;
  content: string;
  autoPopout: boolean;
  announceId: string;
};
```

Add `isSyncPush: boolean;` after `announceId: string;`:
```typescript
export type IAnnouncementItem = {
  publishTime: string;
  title: string;
  content: string;
  autoPopout: boolean;
  announceId: string;
  isSyncPush: boolean;
};
```

### File 2: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-web/packages/web/common/dataConversion/announce.ts`

In `toAnnounce()` function, after `autoPopout: objectPick(v, 'isPopup', false),` add:
```typescript
    isSyncPush: objectPick(v, 'isSyncPush', false),
```

In `announceTo()` function, after `announcementId: v.announceId,` add:
```typescript
    isSyncPush: v.isSyncPush,
```

## Task 7: Add Switch to ModifyAnnouncement

### File: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-web/packages/web/pages/user-backend/upgrade-announcement/ModifyAnnouncement.tsx`

1. Change the import line from:
```typescript
import { Button, DatePicker, Dropdown, Modal } from 'antd';
```
to:
```typescript
import { Button, DatePicker, Dropdown, Modal, Switch } from 'antd';
```

2. After the closing `/>` of the TipTapEditor component (the one with `className="max-h-[450px] mb-2"`), add:
```tsx
        <div className="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <Switch
            size="small"
            checked={inEditingData.isSyncPush}
            onChange={(v) => {
              setInEditingData({
                ...inEditingData,
                isSyncPush: v,
              });
            }}
          />
          <span className="text-sm text-gray-500">
            <I18nText>syncPushHint</I18nText>
          </span>
        </div>
```

## Task 8: i18n

### File 1: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-web/packages/web/i18n/zh-CN.ts`

After line `announceContent: '公告内容',` (around line 737), add:
```typescript
  syncPushLabel: '同步推送',
  syncPushHint: '发布时同步推送到站内通知和MM',
```

### File 2: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-web/packages/web/i18n/en-US.ts`

After line `announceContent: 'Announcement Content',` (around line 736), add:
```typescript
  syncPushLabel: 'Sync Push',
  syncPushHint: 'Push to in-app notification and MM when published',
```

